			text11 = "Limit Cost: " + WildMagicSurge.baseLimitCost + Environment.NewLine;
			text11 = text11 + Environment.NewLine + "In the depths of the void lies Mrs Luck's Casino, a place with only 1 rule: ''The House Always Wins''. Of course, things in motion, stay in motion, and when one man was on a high roll, he almost ran the place out of business. And once he had beat the Casino, he must have been The House, because after all: The House Always Wins...";
